<td><span lang="ar" xml:lang="ar">ـــكِ</span> <span title="DIN 31635 Arabic" class="Unicode" style="white-space:normal; text-decoration: none"><i>—ki</i></span></td>
<td><span lang="ar" xml:lang="ar">تــــِينَ</span> <span title="DIN 31635 Arabic" class="Unicode" style="white-space:normal; text-decoration: none"><i>t—īna</i></span></td>
